WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.000
Public Program, Teesside Polytechnic, Middlesbrough (England), 31 July 1984.

00:02.080 --> 00:06.080
I bow to all the seekers of truth.

00:10.280 --> 00:15.000
First of all, we have to know what truth means.

00:17.080 --> 00:19.000
We want to seek truth,

00:19.000 --> 00:23.240
there’s an urge within us that we have to seek the truth.

00:24.000 --> 00:29.240
Because of this seeking only we all have become human beings.

00:30.000 --> 00:35.000
Now after human beings' stage, what is going to happen to us?

00:35.280 --> 00:40.000
As it is, you find there is so much of confusion in this world,

00:40.080 --> 00:44.000
so much of confusion, so many ideas, so many thoughts,

00:44.000 --> 00:48.000
so many ideologies, so many religions. All kinds of things

00:48.000 --> 00:55.000
have come up and a simple human starts looking at it

00:55.080 --> 00:57.000
and he gets quite puzzled,

00:57.000 --> 00:59.000
“What sort of thing this world is?”

00:59.080 --> 01:02.000
It’s a very confused world, first of all.

01:02.280 --> 01:06.000
The confusion gives you a greater urge to seek,

01:08.080 --> 01:11.000
because you find, “What’s this going on?”

01:11.080 --> 01:14.280
Secondly, I went round your city today

01:15.000 --> 01:17.080
just to vibrate the whole place

01:18.000 --> 01:23.000
and I felt the place has got a kind of a feeling of dullness

01:23.000 --> 01:25.160
and I asked the person who was driving Me,

01:26.000 --> 01:29.160
I said, “Why the people here are looking very dull?”

01:30.000 --> 01:33.000
He said, “The people are now without any jobs,”

01:33.000 --> 01:38.000
so, I said that should happen to any country which is so industrially developed.

01:38.080 --> 01:41.000
When we are industrially developed, you see,

01:41.000 --> 01:45.080
all our industrial wants are over perhaps,

01:46.000 --> 01:47.280
then we start seeking more

01:48.000 --> 01:50.000
because we think now we’ve got everything,

01:50.000 --> 01:54.000
we’ve got proper dress to wear, we’ve got food, we’ve got everything,

01:54.000 --> 01:57.000
now what next? And that’s how we become dull

01:57.080 --> 02:00.080
because we don’t understand the meaning of life.

02:01.000 --> 02:06.000
Now this meaning of life is more in the people who are affluent

02:06.000 --> 02:10.080
and has to be less in the people who are still developing

02:10.280 --> 02:13.000
because they want to become like you,

02:13.000 --> 02:15.000
have all plastics around them,

02:15.000 --> 02:18.000
they want to have foundries with all pollution, everything.

02:18.000 --> 02:21.000
Once they have that then they will start seeking.

02:21.080 --> 02:23.080
But in a country like India

02:24.000 --> 02:26.280
which has been a very different type of a country I say,

02:27.000 --> 02:30.000
because of climatic position. It’s very good climate,

02:30.000 --> 02:34.000
like this, it is always there, so you can be always out in the villages,

02:34.000 --> 02:38.000
you can be in the forest and you don’t have to worry so much

02:38.000 --> 02:43.000
to fight the nature. So in such a place people have been meditating

02:43.000 --> 02:46.000
and trying to find out, “Why are we here?”

02:47.000 --> 02:50.000
Now all these things when you see the development everywhere,

02:50.000 --> 02:54.080
you find it’s like the tree, the tree outside you see very well developed.

02:54.280 --> 02:59.000
But any tree that has developed very much must have very deep roots,

02:59.000 --> 03:02.000
otherwise it will be all finished and destroyed.

03:02.080 --> 03:05.080
So when there is such a lot of development outside,

03:05.240 --> 03:09.000
there must have been some development inside also, the roots.

03:09.000 --> 03:13.000
And this is what we are going to tell you about the roots now

03:13.000 --> 03:16.000
because your development is sufficiently enough and if

03:16.000 --> 03:20.080
you have to sustain this development you must know about your roots.

03:21.000 --> 03:23.000
We have neglected our roots very much

03:23.000 --> 03:26.000
and that’s the reason today we also find people suffering

03:26.000 --> 03:29.000
from terminal diseases and all kinds of trouble.

03:29.000 --> 03:31.000
That is one of the first worry for Me

03:31.080 --> 03:33.080
that everyone should be healthy

03:34.000 --> 03:38.160
and that health comes to you not from outside, from inside.

03:39.000 --> 03:42.080
Because supposing if on a tree you find a leaf is sick

03:42.280 --> 03:45.080
and you start treating the leaf, you don’t treat the tree.

03:45.160 --> 03:47.000
You don’t treat the disease at all.

03:47.080 --> 03:51.000
But if you have some means of entering into the roots, you treat

03:51.080 --> 03:57.000
the whole of that tree very well, very easily in a very simple manner.

03:57.280 --> 04:01.000
In the same way if you can somehow reach your roots,

04:01.080 --> 04:08.000
you can treat yourself without much difficulty, without any medicine also.

04:08.080 --> 04:10.000
Now where are these roots?

04:10.080 --> 04:12.000
Uh, for that you have to see to this chart,

04:12.080 --> 04:15.000
I don’t know if everybody can see this chart,

04:15.000 --> 04:19.000
that within us this beautiful instrument is placed,

04:19.000 --> 04:23.000
and this is what is described in the Bible as the tree of life.

04:23.080 --> 04:30.080
Unless and until you achieve a state which we call as self-realization,

04:30.080 --> 04:34.000
which Christ called as the second birth

04:35.000 --> 04:37.080
we cannot understand what is this.

04:37.160 --> 04:41.000
