04:41.000 --> 04:45.000
but if I say, “Pay attention to yourself within,” you cannot.

04:46.000 --> 04:49.000
It’s a difficult thing, our attention is outside.

04:49.000 --> 04:51.000
Now what should happen for that?

04:51.000 --> 04:53.000
There’s a happening that takes place,

04:53.000 --> 04:57.160
because of that happening your attention is attracted inside.

04:58.000 --> 04:59.240
