04:59.240 --> 05:04.080
the same attention gets the enlightenment of this power

05:04.080 --> 05:08.000
which is within you, us in the sacrum bone,

05:08.000 --> 05:12.000
sacrum meaning sacred, that means the Greeks knew about it.

05:12.000 --> 05:17.080
When this power rises, awakens, it’s like the plumule in the seed,

05:17.080 --> 05:20.000
the germinating power of a seed

05:20.000 --> 05:24.000
and it just gives you a new dimension.

05:25.000 --> 05:27.080
It enriches your subtle centers.

05:28.000 --> 05:35.000
These subtle centers actually are the subtle entities of the gross plexuses.

05:36.000 --> 05:38.280
