05:45.080 --> 05:48.000
how we get a particular disease called horrible cancer

05:49.000 --> 05:51.000
and that is so common in the West,

05:51.280 --> 05:56.000
not so much in the developing countries as it is here.

05:56.000 --> 05:59.000
They say cancer is a rich man’s disease.

06:00.080 --> 06:06.000
The thing is that within us there are two systems,

06:06.280 --> 06:10.000
of nervous systems which cater us.

06:11.000 --> 06:14.000
One of them is the one called as the central nervous system

06:14.080 --> 06:18.000
another is the one which we call as autonomous nervous system.

06:18.280 --> 06:22.000
Now the doctors are honest, they just call it by name, autonomous.

06:22.000 --> 06:26.000
Now if you ask them, “Who is this auto,” they won’t be able to tell you.

06:27.000 --> 06:29.000
Just they call it some name, autonomous.

06:29.240 --> 06:32.080
This auto is the Spirit in the heart

06:33.000 --> 06:38.000
and this auto if you somehow or other bring into your attention

06:38.000 --> 06:40.280
the light of the auto comes into your attention,

06:41.000 --> 06:43.280
you start controlling your being completely.

06:45.000 --> 06:47.000
This is a simple method I’m telling you.

06:47.080 --> 06:50.000
Now the nature of the roots is such

06:50.000 --> 06:55.000
that this autonomous nervous system has three channels.

06:55.080 --> 06:58.240
The two channels of the left and the right sympathetic nervous system

06:59.000 --> 07:03.000
and the central one is the parasympathetic. Now you can see here

07:03.000 --> 07:05.000
the three channels but these are the subtle channels

07:05.160 --> 07:12.000
which control, which control the gross channels.

07:12.000 --> 07:16.080
Now these subtle channels work out in such a way

07:16.080 --> 07:20.000
that the left-side channel caters to your past,

07:20.080 --> 07:24.000
caters to what has happened, caters to your conditioning

07:24.000 --> 07:28.080
It is what we call is the channel of the moon,

07:29.000 --> 07:34.000
or this is the one that works out the power of desire within us.

07:35.000 --> 07:40.000
The right-side channel is the channel which works out the action,

07:40.000 --> 07:43.240
so it is the channel of the action, caters to your future,

07:44.000 --> 07:47.160
to your mental activities and to your physical activities.

07:48.000 --> 07:50.240
It is called as the channel of the sun.

07:51.000 --> 07:56.000
Now both of them are parallel to each other.

07:56.240 --> 08:00.080
Now when a human being tries to find out something,

08:00.080 --> 08:04.000
