08:04.000 --> 08:08.000
Supposing he goes to the pub then he must drink the whole of it.

08:09.000 --> 08:12.240
If he goes to some other work, he must finish off his work with

08:13.000 --> 08:18.000
completely dedication, as they call it and exhaust all his life doing that.

08:18.000 --> 08:22.160
Always we go to extremes, either to the left or to the right.

08:23.000 --> 08:28.160
Now if a person is a person of moderation, he stays in the center.

08:29.000 --> 08:32.000
The central path is for our evolution.

08:33.000 --> 08:36.280
The whole of matter has evolved, as you know there’s a chart

08:37.000 --> 08:41.000
