09:10.000 --> 09:12.000
and we become human beings.

09:13.080 --> 09:16.080
Now the question comes, what next?

09:17.000 --> 09:18.080
Why are we here?

09:19.000 --> 09:22.000
We are human beings but what are we to achieve next.

09:23.000 --> 09:25.160
If this question doesn’t come into your mind

09:26.000 --> 09:28.000
then it will come later on, no doubt,

09:28.000 --> 09:32.000
but it’s better that the time is here for you to seek that;

09:32.000 --> 09:35.000
why are we on this earth?

09:35.000 --> 09:39.000
We are here on this earth, like this instrument if you make,

09:39.000 --> 09:42.000
