all the religions came on this earth to establish that balance within.

19:11.000 --> 19:16.000
Religions, all of them came on this earth to establish that balance.

19:16.000 --> 19:19.080
Why the balance, again the question can come up, why the balance.

19:19.240 --> 19:22.000
The balance is for our ultimate ascent,

19:22.000 --> 19:28.000
for example, if you have to take an aero plane, ascend it,

19:28.000 --> 19:30.000
you have to first see if it is balanced or not,

19:30.000 --> 19:33.000
otherwise, it will be not floating horizontally

19:33.000 --> 19:38.000
but it might go one-sided, you see so one has to have a balance in life.

19:38.000 --> 19:43.000
But if you read yourself, if you face yourself you will understand that,

19:43.000 --> 19:46.000
“No, we are not so much balanced as we should have been.”

19:46.000 --> 19:50.000
So this balance has to be brought in, in human beings

19:50.000 --> 19:54.000
and that’s why we had great prophets on this earth

19:54.080 --> 19:56.000
to teach us the balance.

19:56.000 --> 20:00.000
And these prophets came at a time where we needed this balance,

20:00.160 --> 20:04.000
at every time people became imbalanced, they came on this earth

20:04.000 --> 20:06.000
to teach us balance.

20:06.000 --> 20:10.000
When this balance is lost, mostly we develop diseases.

20:10.000 --> 20:14.000
Even in religious things we can be very imbalanced.

20:14.000 --> 20:17.000
Like I’ve seen people reading Bible for three hours,

20:17.000 --> 20:19.000
what is the need to read Bible?

20:19.080 --> 20:22.000
I mean, for three hours you don’t learn anything.

20:22.000 --> 20:26.000
Actually, if you understand religion, is not to be read,

20:26.000 --> 20:29.000
but to be felt and experienced within yourself.

20:29.000 --> 20:33.000
Religion is like the ten valences of human beings.

20:34.000 --> 20:36.000
And the ten valences of the human beings

20:36.000 --> 20:39.000
when we lose the valence, we lose our balance.

20:39.160 --> 20:42.000
Now anything like, say a country

20:42.000 --> 20:44.000
which is over-developed loses its balance.

20:44.080 --> 20:47.000
A country which is under-developed also can lose its balance.

20:47.240 --> 20:49.080
Anywhere it can happen the same way,

20:49.280 --> 20:52.280
makes no difference whether you’re developed or under-developed,

20:53.000 --> 20:57.000
you are in the same way whether the balance is up or down,

20:57.000 --> 20:59.000
makes no difference. So it is like that.

21:00.000 --> 21:02.000
Now with the Kundalini what happens,

21:02.000 --> 21:05.000
the first thing it does is to create the balance within.

21:06.000 --> 21:11.000
When She rises in that part of the thing, area of the stomach

21:11.000 --> 21:14.000
it creates the balance, it brings forth the balance.

21:14.000 --> 21:19.000
Once the balance has come then it’s much easier for you

21:19.000 --> 21:22.160
to balance all the chakras which have gone upside down

21:23.000 --> 21:26.000
or which are crooked and the balance comes and fix them together.

21:27.000 --> 21:31.080
With that balance the chakras get their forms all right

21:31.280 --> 21:34.000
and because of that the Kundalini rises.

21:34.000 --> 21:38.000
She rises and pierces through your fontanelle bone area

21:38.000 --> 21:40.160
which is the true baptism.

21:41.000 --> 21:43.000
It’s not like somebody coming putting water onto your head

21:43.000 --> 21:45.160
and say, “Now you’re baptized.” And we accept it.

21:46.000 --> 21:50.000
It’s just an exercise, there’s no truth about it.

21:50.240 --> 21:55.000
The cool breeze of the Holy Ghost has to be felt on top of your head.

21:55.280 --> 22:01.000
So the truth has to be felt on your central nervous system,

22:01.000 --> 22:04.080
that means you must feel them on your fingertips.

22:05.000 --> 22:07.000
Mohamad Sahib has clearly said that

22:07.000 --> 22:11.000
at the time of Resurrection your hands will speak.

22:11.000 --> 22:13.000
But nobody wants to talk of Resurrection,

22:13.160 --> 22:17.000
nobody wants to talk of something that is good to happen,

22:17.000 --> 22:22.000
that there will be a period where people will be redeemed,

22:22.000 --> 22:25.000
that there will be a Redeemer, there will be a Counsellor;

22:25.000 --> 22:27.000
nobody wants to talk of that.

22:27.000 --> 22:30.080
They want to talk of the doomsday because people will be frightened

22:30.280 --> 22:33.000
and they’ll be pouring money for them.

22:33.000 --> 22:38.000
It’s a money-making fright which is created in people.

22:38.280 --> 22:42.080
The God Almighty who has created this beautiful universe

22:43.000 --> 22:46.000
has created you as special people who are human beings,

22:46.000 --> 22:53.000
do you think He’s going to allow us to destroy His great creation?

22:53.000 --> 22:56.000
He’s made us so beautifully within ourselves

22:56.000 --> 23:02.000
and we have to just understand that you’re not what you seem to be,

23:02.000 --> 23:06.160
you’re much greater, you’re much more, you are glorified by Him.

23:07.000 --> 23:10.280
Because only this thing has to happen and once it happens

23:11.000 --> 23:16.000
you’ll be surprised that you become in charge of yourself,

23:16.240 --> 23:20.160
that you become empowered with that power of God

23:21.000 --> 23:22.240
which flows through you.

23:23.000 --> 23:28.000
You can cure people, you can help people, you can raise Kundalini,

23:28.000 --> 23:31.000
you can get rid of all these stupid problems,

23:31.080 --> 23:35.080
all these big problems and all the universal problems

23:36.000 --> 23:38.000
because a transformation takes place within you.

23:39.080 --> 23:42.280
We had an alcoholic in Brighton one day,

23:43.000 --> 23:46.000
he came to the program completely drunk and he started abusing Me.

23:46.240 --> 23:51.000
I just smiled at him. Next day he came and he got his realization.

23:51.000 --> 23:54.000
Today he’s a first-class man, he’s earning such a lot of money,

23:54.080 --> 23:56.000
he’s doing so well.

23:56.000 --> 24:00.000
So what happens to you that you become yourself

24:00.000 --> 24:04.000
and to become yourself means you become the Spirit,

24:04.000 --> 24:08.000
and Spirit is the reflection of God within yourself.

24:08.000 --> 24:12.000
Once that happens, you become the dynamic power of God

24:12.000 --> 24:15.080
and you’re surprised the miraculous way you’re helped.

24:16.000 --> 24:19.080
Now of course, Sahaja Yoga has definitely cured cancer, no doubt,

24:20.000 --> 24:22.000
it can cure so many diseases.

24:22.000 --> 24:24.280
But when we wrote to the British council about it

24:25.000 --> 24:27.080
and they found out that we were curing people, they said,

24:28.000 --> 24:32.000
“There’s a big red tape going on,” they’ve to go through the files,

24:32.000 --> 24:34.000
they have to find out, this, that.

24:34.000 --> 24:38.000
So we said, “All right, doesn’t matter, let them have their own time.”

24:38.000 --> 24:41.000
But Sahaja Yoga is not only for physical being

24:41.160 --> 24:43.000
because you are not only physical being.

24:43.000 --> 24:46.000
I tell you there are many wrestlers and boxers

24:46.000 --> 24:49.240
who come to Me and say, “Mother,” who are very, very sturdy people,

24:50.000 --> 24:52.000
they say, “Mother, we have no peace, give us peace.”

24:52.240 --> 24:56.240
So it is not for physical being, it is not for mental being,

24:57.000 --> 25:01.000
it’s not for emotional being but it is for your spiritual being.

25:01.000 --> 25:05.000
But as you’re the temple of God, the temple has to be cleansed.

25:05.000 --> 25:08.000
When some guest is coming to your house, we clean the house,

25:08.080 --> 25:11.000
make it beautiful, put flowers, decorate it.

25:11.000 --> 25:15.160
In the same way, when your Spirit is going to enter into your attention

25:16.000 --> 25:19.000
your body has to be cleansed; your mind has to be purified

25:19.000 --> 25:24.240
and that you have to become a beautiful temple for that enlightenment.

25:25.000 --> 25:29.280
And that’s how as a by-product of this Kundalini awakening you get cured.

25:30.120 --> 25:32.200
Now what happens to your awareness,

25:32.200 --> 25:35.000
that you become collectively conscious.

25:35.000 --> 25:37.080
You become, again I say there’s no certificate.

25:37.080 --> 25:39.320
In Sahaja Yoga there’s no membership,

25:40.080 --> 25:43.080
of course you must have heard, there’s no money to be paid or anything.

25:43.120 --> 25:45.280
I mean, it is stupid, how can you pay money to God,

25:45.280 --> 25:47.160
what does He understand about money?

25:47.200 --> 25:50.080
How much money are you going to pay for yourself, first of all?

25:50.120 --> 25:53.080
He has given beautiful eyes to us, what do we pay Him, nothing;

25:53.080 --> 25:55.040
on the contrary we spoil them all the time

25:55.080 --> 25:58.280
by looking at things with lust and greed, we spoil them.

25:59.080 --> 26:02.240
We have adultery in our eyes, so we spoil them, the beautiful

26:02.280 --> 26:06.040
innocent eyes that He has given us, the pure eyes, we spoil them.

26:06.080 --> 26:09.280
But when you’re awakened, your eyes become so beautiful

26:09.320 --> 26:12.160
that you look at the person, the person gets all right.

26:13.280 --> 26:18.080
Your presence, merely your presence can help so many.

26:18.320 --> 26:21.000
But you have to achieve that state.

26:21.080 --> 26:25.120
Now as he said, you cannot demand it, you see, there’s no shop here.

26:25.240 --> 26:27.280
In a shop you pay the money so you can demand,

26:27.280 --> 26:30.200
“All right, come along, this was bad and I paid so much money.”

26:30.280 --> 26:35.280
But here what do you give? Your seeking, you’re seeking the higher being,

26:35.320 --> 26:38.080
you are not seeking your cure but you’re seeking

26:38.120 --> 26:40.040
the higher being within you.

26:40.080 --> 26:43.280
The property, the wealth of spirituality that resides in all of us.

26:44.040 --> 26:50.080
It is there, it is all there, only thing we have to pay attention to it and get it.

26:50.280 --> 26:53.280
Now you become collectively conscious means you start feeling

26:53.280 --> 26:56.080
other people on your fingertips.

26:56.240 --> 26:59.200
Even a child can say, “This is the problem, this is the problem,”

26:59.200 --> 27:02.080
now you have to just know what these denote

27:02.080 --> 27:05.080
and that’s what I have decoded that this means heart,

27:05.080 --> 27:08.080
this means something else, this means something else

27:08.080 --> 27:11.080
and all the centers, the five and the sixth and the seventh centers,

27:11.120 --> 27:13.000
on the left and the right-hand side.

27:13.080 --> 27:16.080
So immediately you’ll know the person’s suffering.

27:16.200 --> 27:20.040
But we don’t talk like doctors, we don’t say,

27:20.080 --> 27:22.120
“This fellow is egoistical,” not like that.

27:22.200 --> 27:24.320
But we’ll say, “His Agnya chakra in the front is catching,”

27:25.080 --> 27:27.240
that means he’s egoistical. But we don’t say that.

27:27.240 --> 27:30.080
Even a person will come and say, “Mother today my Agnya is catching,

27:30.120 --> 27:32.280
just take it out,” meaning, “I’ve been egoistical.”

27:33.120 --> 27:37.000
So the language is different as you must have read in the Bible

27:37.080 --> 27:39.280
that when they got their realization through the Holy Ghost

27:39.280 --> 27:42.040
they started speaking in strange languages.

27:42.080 --> 27:46.080
That doesn’t mean that they started speaking in Latin or Hebrew.

27:46.080 --> 27:51.080
It means that they started speaking in the languages of chakras,

27:51.160 --> 27:53.280
of centers, of the subtle centers.

27:54.040 --> 27:57.200
They started talking about the channels,

27:57.240 --> 28:00.280
because you become subtle, you start seeing something subtle.

28:00.320 --> 28:03.320
Like the way you see colors, animals do not see.

28:04.080 --> 28:07.080
The way you see filth and dirt the animals do not see.

28:07.160 --> 28:11.080
But when you become realized souls you see the dirt and filth of a

28:11.240 --> 28:17.000
much subtler nature. That is the sin that they call it or anything like that.

28:17.080 --> 28:19.080
So you become separated from this,

28:19.120 --> 28:22.160
and you start witnessing the whole world like a witness.

28:22.200 --> 28:26.120
You become collectively conscious, so supposing you get cured,

28:26.200 --> 28:31.080
so-called by Me, so-called, I would say, then there’s no obligation

28:31.080 --> 28:34.080
because if you’re part and parcel of Me, whom do I help?

28:34.160 --> 28:38.080
If this finger is paining and I rub it like this, whom do I help,

28:38.120 --> 28:40.080
I help Myself, isn’t it?

28:40.160 --> 28:42.320
So you become part and parcel of the whole

28:43.080 --> 28:45.080
and when you become part and parcel of the whole,

28:45.160 --> 28:48.160
the whole thing works out in such a homogenous way.

28:48.280 --> 28:51.200
As a result of that the people in England

28:51.240 --> 28:55.080
who were suffering from many diseases, people in Australia,

28:55.080 --> 28:57.040
so many countries now we have,

28:57.080 --> 29:01.200
most of the European countries we have tackled, have been cured.

29:03.120 --> 29:06.280
They have been cured of their diseases, of their ailments,

29:07.000 --> 29:09.240
they’ve become so powerful that they have no habits,

29:10.080 --> 29:13.240
nothing can deter them. They’re very joyous, happy people,

29:13.280 --> 29:17.000
if you see their photographs, you’ll say they’re lotuses sitting down

29:17.080 --> 29:21.040
beautifully pink. And the same thing is happening in India

29:21.080 --> 29:25.240
where I’m working for a much shorter time than I have worked in England.

29:26.000 --> 29:29.160
England has a special place; I must say because in the universe

29:29.200 --> 29:32.160
England is the heart of the universe.

29:33.120 --> 29:35.280
Perhaps you do not realize, you’re not aware of it.

29:36.080 --> 29:38.080
But English are very balanced people compared to

29:38.160 --> 29:41.280
all other Western people, I must say. But despite that

29:42.040 --> 29:44.280
sometimes you go off because you’ve lost your confidence,

29:45.080 --> 29:47.280
you try to follow French, you try to follow Americans,

29:48.000 --> 29:50.120
they have to follow you, not that you have to follow them.

29:51.000 --> 29:52.200
You can articulate.

29:52.280 --> 29:55.120
Now once upon a time it was the industrial development

29:55.160 --> 29:59.240
and all these things were there, so you articulated into these

30:00.080 --> 30:05.120
but now that is over. Now it has to be spiritual development,

30:05.240 --> 30:10.040
for that also I think one has to work out in England.

30:10.120 --> 30:13.160
And that’s how perhaps My husband got elected to this job

30:13.240 --> 30:16.160
and had to come to England. I’ve been here for ten years

30:16.200 --> 30:19.320
while in India I was just two years after I started My work.

30:20.080 --> 30:24.080
Of course I travel all over and the most wonderful thing I’ve found out

30:24.160 --> 30:29.160
about the Western people is that their hankering is no more now

30:29.200 --> 30:34.080
for material things. It looks little bit but is not so much.

30:34.200 --> 30:36.320
Once they get to their realization, they want to save others,

30:37.040 --> 30:38.200
they want to help others.

30:38.240 --> 30:42.160
Now all the way Dr. Warren has come from Australia.

30:42.280 --> 30:45.080
Now they said the psychology is such

30:45.080 --> 30:49.080
if the Australians talk to the English, they feel happy.

30:49.160 --> 30:54.160
So we sent English to America and you’ll be surprised that in Houston

30:54.240 --> 30:57.080
an Englishman went there and he was regarded as a very

30:57.080 --> 31:00.280
respectable man, you see, and they all listened to him nicely.

31:01.040 --> 31:05.320
It’s a funny psychology but we have great Sahaja Yogis even in England.

31:06.080 --> 31:10.200
In England we have very great people who have mastered this art

31:10.320 --> 31:14.120
and once you know this you become so scholarly

31:14.200 --> 31:15.200
that many a times

31:15.200 --> 31:17.080
these newspaper people ask Me,

31:17.120 --> 31:22.240
“Have you got all your disciples as scholars?”

31:23.080 --> 31:25.280
I said, “No, they’re not My disciples, they’re children.”

31:26.040 --> 31:29.280
But they become scholarly because they get to the essence of knowledge

31:30.000 --> 31:32.000
and this is the true knowledge.

31:32.080 --> 31:35.320
The otherwise whatever knowledge we have is of the dead.

31:36.080 --> 31:40.080
For example I was looking at your foundries, what do we do?

31:40.080 --> 31:43.040
We take out the dead and make something out of it.

31:44.320 --> 31:48.320
Can we make anything living? Can we transform these flowers into fruits?

31:49.080 --> 31:54.040
We cannot. After realization you start doing the living work

31:54.080 --> 31:59.240
and this is the process which a living work of living God.

32:00.080 --> 32:02.320
So you just cannot say that, “I stand on my head

32:03.080 --> 32:06.320
and I get the Kundalini there,” or, “I cut my hair short or

32:07.080 --> 32:11.080
I have another kind of a dress.” It’s nothing outside.

32:11.120 --> 32:15.160
It’s inside the happening takes place and you become another person.

32:15.240 --> 32:20.320
In Sanskrit language we call a bird as dwijaha, means born again

32:21.080 --> 32:25.120
and a Brahmin, the one who has known the power of Brahma,

32:25.200 --> 32:28.240
the power of God’s love, is called also dwijaha.

32:28.280 --> 32:31.240
Dwijaha, means the one who is born again.

32:32.040 --> 32:37.080
Now a bird is first is an egg and then it becomes a bird.

32:37.280 --> 32:43.120
That’s why you’ll be surprised that Christ when He was crucified

32:43.240 --> 32:48.160
and when He was resurrected on the Easter day it is to show

32:48.240 --> 32:53.280
that a person leaves this material body and becomes the Spirit.

32:54.080 --> 32:58.080
Resurrection is the message of Christ which is a very great thing

32:58.080 --> 33:02.360
He achieved because He was nothing but Himself the Brahma,

33:03.080 --> 33:06.400
the Chaitanya, Omkara, what you call the word. So that’s why He could

33:07.040 --> 33:10.320
achieve that thing. It’s all written about Him in Indian Scriptures.

33:11.040 --> 33:13.080
You have to go out to see all these things,

33:13.120 --> 33:15.280
what is the thing written about Christ.

33:15.360 --> 33:18.080
Bible cannot contain Him within Himself

33:18.080 --> 33:21.080
and the four years life that He led in this misery

33:21.280 --> 33:25.040
is not representative of His whole background.

33:25.080 --> 33:27.240
If you have to know about His background you have to read

33:27.280 --> 33:30.160
some books which were written fourteen thousand years back.

33:30.280 --> 33:35.280
They have told about that. So when He resurrected what we do,

33:35.320 --> 33:42.200
we present an egg on the Easter Sunday. What does that mean?

33:42.280 --> 33:47.080
That on an Easter Sunday you’re an egg and on the Easter Monday

33:47.160 --> 33:53.080
you are the bird. But we don’t know, we do it just automatically

33:53.160 --> 33:56.320
without understanding why we give those eggs to people.

33:57.120 --> 34:00.320
This is what we have to understand. Even to understand Bible

34:01.000 --> 34:04.280
we have to be self-realized, even to understand the life of Christ

34:04.320 --> 34:08.240
which was just so great we have to be realized.

34:08.280 --> 34:12.080
Now the controversy about Christ has started, it really pains Me

34:12.080 --> 34:15.080
that these people don’t want to take their realization,

34:15.080 --> 34:20.120
otherwise how can you explain to them any miracle whatsoever?

34:21.240 --> 34:22.400
Life is full of miracles.

34:23.080 --> 34:26.120
Even in My lifetime people have seen miracles happening.

34:26.280 --> 34:31.040
I don’t know if they have brought the photograph. Once I was giving

34:31.080 --> 34:35.160
a lecture in a very remote village where there was a very great soul

34:35.240 --> 34:38.280
who had died. And as soon as I entered the village I told them,

34:38.320 --> 34:40.200
“Who was the great soul who lived here?”

34:40.280 --> 34:42.320
They said he was a Muslim called as Mian.

34:43.080 --> 34:47.240
And I sat down for My lecture and suddenly I found that I got connected

34:47.280 --> 34:50.280
and there was a big light on My head coming.

34:50.320 --> 34:54.280
And then I saw it seven times the light was there and I got connected

34:54.360 --> 34:58.080
and it showed that, that he was there with Me.

34:58.240 --> 35:02.000
And then suddenly I stopped it, like this laughing.

35:02.120 --> 35:06.320
Imagine the photograph was taken by one girl

35:07.040 --> 35:09.240
and all these seven stages were clearly shown

35:09.280 --> 35:11.080
and you could see the light there.

35:11.080 --> 35:13.360
Now these boys went to show to someone, they said,

35:14.000 --> 35:16.120
“Oh, you must have arranged all these in the village.”

35:16.280 --> 35:20.280
But it was not, in that remote village there is no electricity also.

35:21.080 --> 35:23.280
So where’s the question of… and why should we arrange that?

35:23.320 --> 35:27.280
There are so many miracles that have taken place in Sahaja Yoga,

35:27.360 --> 35:29.080
so many miracles.

35:29.200 --> 35:31.400
I mean the President of India was cured of his cancer

35:32.080 --> 35:33.320
in five minutes, you won’t believe it.

35:34.080 --> 35:36.080
He came to London from his operation

35:36.160 --> 35:39.040
and it was very unsuccessful and he was going to die.

35:39.160 --> 35:41.320
And because of My husband I went to see him.

35:42.080 --> 35:44.240
We knew him otherwise but he didn’t know Me

35:44.240 --> 35:46.040
that I was also Mataji Nirmala Devi

35:46.120 --> 35:48.080
because I don’t tell this to these bureaucrats,

35:48.200 --> 35:50.080
they’re rather difficult people.

35:50.200 --> 35:52.320
So it so happened that one of the…

35:52.440 --> 35:56.200
that was B. K. Nehru who was the High Commissioner,

35:56.200 --> 36:00.160
he told, “Do you know this lady is Mataji Nirmala Devi?”

36:00.320 --> 36:03.240
And the wife of the President had heard My name

36:03.280 --> 36:05.320
as Mataji Nirmala Devi also

36:06.200 --> 36:09.160
and she said, “Mataji, why don’t you cure my husband?”

36:09.440 --> 36:13.200
And he said, “Yes I didn’t know you were Mataji Nirmala Devi.”

36:13.240 --> 36:16.080
I said, “All right.” So I put My hand on his back.

36:16.080 --> 36:19.400
In five minutes…, he could not sleep, he was so much with pain.

36:20.000 --> 36:22.400
He said, ”I’m feeling so relieved I want to lie down and sleep.”

36:23.080 --> 36:26.120
He went off to sleep. They had prepared for his cremation

36:26.200 --> 36:29.080
and everything in India and a big show was there, imagine,

36:29.080 --> 36:31.080
and they reached with the ambulance there.

36:31.240 --> 36:34.080
And there he walked down the steps and they saw him, they thought,

36:34.080 --> 36:36.200
“Is this his ghost walking or what?”

36:36.240 --> 36:39.240
He told Me all the story in a very jocular way

36:39.320 --> 36:44.320
and he said that, “I don’t know, I went, after that I forgot that I was sick

36:44.360 --> 36:49.360
and I went on a tour.” And next year when I went his wife showed Me

36:49.400 --> 36:53.320
that even the mark of the operation had gone, but I must say he must

36:53.400 --> 36:58.120
have been a very great soul to get that way, in such a simple way.

36:58.200 --> 37:01.240
And then he said, “You must have Mother some land because you must

37:01.240 --> 37:04.080
have some place where people should meet you.”

37:04.200 --> 37:06.240
And so he allotted some land to us

37:06.320 --> 37:08.400
and that’s how now we have some land in Delhi.

37:08.400 --> 37:14.280
But what I’m trying to tell you that miracles are the nature of God.

37:14.320 --> 37:17.400
For human beings He’s miraculous, isn’t it? He’s not human being,

37:18.080 --> 37:20.080
how can we judge Him with our limited brain?

37:20.200 --> 37:23.480
He can do whatever He likes and He is full of miracles.

37:24.080 --> 37:26.240
These intellectuals cannot understand Him.

37:26.280 --> 37:29.040
For example, Paul, he was an intellectual,

37:29.080 --> 37:32.120
he was no way a free man, he was not a realized soul

37:32.280 --> 37:35.080
and how can he understand Christ, he cannot.

37:35.120 --> 37:38.080
Because he was just an organizer and intellectual.

37:38.320 --> 37:42.000
You have to be a realized soul and you’ll be surprised Khalil Gibran

37:42.080 --> 37:46.080
has clearly written about Paul if you read him because Khalil Gibran

37:46.080 --> 37:49.280
was a realized soul that, “I can’t understand this strange man

37:49.400 --> 37:53.080
and he’s not a free soul,” and how is he in Bible?

37:53.160 --> 37:57.040
When I first saw the Bible I was surprised. I said, “How is he here?

37:57.200 --> 38:01.080
Who is he? I have never known him.” That’s what it is

38:01.200 --> 38:04.240
but we get enamored by his organizing capacity,

38:04.240 --> 38:08.400
the way he’s organized everything. You cannot organize God, can you?

38:09.280 --> 38:13.040
How can you organize God? Nobody should feel shattered because

38:13.160 --> 38:17.120
they are saying they were not miracles and they were allegories.

38:17.200 --> 38:22.320
You will meet so many miracles as soon as you will become the Spirit.

38:23.080 --> 38:24.320
God is full of miracles.

38:24.400 --> 38:28.120
Every miracle that is described of Christ is true.

38:28.440 --> 38:34.000
It was an immaculate conception. And we have His previous life,

38:34.080 --> 38:37.280
we know how He was created on this earth through complete

38:37.320 --> 38:42.080
immaculate conception by a virgin and everything we know about it

38:42.080 --> 38:46.240
in India and Indians are shocked how could you accept such a nonsense

38:46.320 --> 38:50.200
from people who are just intellectuals, they’re not realized souls.

38:50.360 --> 38:55.240
Thank God in India even today people know what is a realized soul is.

38:55.440 --> 38:59.200
Even the president, he would not sit down when I went to see him.

