39:05.080 --> 39:08.320
he wouldn’t sit with Me on the same couch which he was having.

39:09.080 --> 39:13.080
That’s what it is. Our sensitivity in the West is gone down

39:13.080 --> 39:17.080
because of intellectualism. Even the science is a barrier,

39:17.160 --> 39:20.400
all these things are barriers, you see, and this barrier we must

39:21.080 --> 39:23.320
understand we have to become the same innocent person

39:23.400 --> 39:27.240
as Christ has said that you have to become children

39:27.240 --> 39:30.480
to enter into the kingdom of God. And this happens to you

39:31.080 --> 39:33.320
as soon as the Kundalini rises you become innocent,

39:33.480 --> 39:37.080
you become an innocent person. Innocent doesn’t mean a fool,

39:37.120 --> 39:41.520
innocent is the most intelligent, is the most powerful person.

39:42.240 --> 39:46.440
And a person who is a realized soul is also not a compromising person,

39:46.480 --> 39:49.240
“All right, if the churches are not working

