It was He who stood against the people who were trying

40:22.000 --> 40:27.320
to throw stones at a prostitute and challenging because He knew

40:27.400 --> 40:31.480
that everybody was sinful and nobody had right to judge others.

40:32.240 --> 40:35.320
It was His power that made Him stand against all of them.

