I would say anyone of these who talk against Christ like this

40:39.280 --> 40:42.440
should stand up and say it. Have they got courage?

40:42.520 --> 40:46.400
They have no courage and that’s why I say they are not free people,

40:46.520 --> 40:48.000
they’re bound.

