But by giving them their realization, their property, what they have.

40:58.440 --> 41:02.320
They don’t want to accept it because they think they’ll be challenged.

41:02.480 --> 41:06.320
They all can get realization themselves but they will not come forward.

41:06.400 --> 41:10.320
So don’t believe when they say that there were no miracles of Christ.

41:10.480 --> 41:14.280
Without miracles how are we created; ourselves we are miraculous.

41:14.360 --> 41:19.280
Think of ourselves; we are made like a computer which doesn’t think,

41:19.320 --> 41:22.080
it doesn’t need any programming. When you are seeing Me,

41:22.080 --> 41:25.320
you are seeing Me, you don’t have to think about it, isn’t it?

41:27.120 --> 41:31.280
What a great computer we are made. Can they make even a flower?

41:31.400 --> 41:35.560
What are they talking of intellectualizing and the miracles of miracles

41:36.080 --> 41:40.360
that are so many, how we are channelized, how we are born,

41:40.480 --> 41:46.080
how out of thousands of genes, one gene is used for the eyes,

41:46.200 --> 41:49.320
one for the nose, how they develop into a particular thing.

41:49.360 --> 41:51.560
Just look at the miracle of the whole universe,

41:52.080 --> 41:56.040
we don’t want to see that because we are becoming egoistical about it.

41:56.240 --> 42:00.320
We think that we can manage God, we can organize Him,

42:00.400 --> 42:05.280
we can do whatever we like. In the same realm, when we start seeing

42:05.360 --> 42:09.000
the horrible people coming from India and looting you,

42:09.080 --> 42:12.480
we succumb to them because they pamper your ego. They say,

42:12.520 --> 42:16.440
“All right, you can pay for me” “Oh, we can buy him, he’s for sale.”

42:16.520 --> 42:20.240
And now, I was surprised among the elite societies, it’s very funny

42:20.320 --> 42:26.160
but it’s true, they discuss, “I think this guru is three pounds less,”

42:27.000 --> 42:30.400
or, “That guru you can say five pounds,” it’s a big discussion on.

42:30.480 --> 42:32.480
It’s a guru-shopping going on, you see.

