I’ve been talking against them for the last twelve years

42:36.280 --> 42:39.240
openly taking their names and blasting them.

42:39.280 --> 42:44.040
About this Scientology, I told them in Brighton two years back

42:44.360 --> 42:46.480
and now they’ve found out about this Scientology.

42:47.040 --> 42:50.440
So the Brighton radio was very kind to Me and they called Me.

42:50.480 --> 42:53.360
I said, “When I told you, you were the ones who blasted Me,

42:53.440 --> 42:56.160
then why should you say this against Scientology?”

42:56.320 --> 42:59.560
Anybody who takes money from you in the name of God,

43:00.040 --> 43:04.400
know that he is a devil. No one should take any money

43:04.440 --> 43:07.280
in the name of God. All right you have to have the hall,

43:07.320 --> 43:11.440
you pay for the hall not for God. If your climate was all right,

43:11.480 --> 43:15.040
we could have done it outside but paying for the hall

43:15.080 --> 43:19.320
is different from paying for God. And the way these people have

43:19.360 --> 43:22.480
minted money is your naiveness, your stupidity, I should say

43:23.040 --> 43:26.080
that you didn’t understand this simple thing that these people are

43:26.160 --> 43:31.480
buying lots of aero planes and Rolls-Royces and you’re paying for it.

43:32.040 --> 43:34.440
Still I must say, English are wiser than many others.

43:35.080 --> 43:37.160
Like in America, I went and they told Me,

43:37.200 --> 43:39.080
“How many Rolls-Royces she has?”

43:39.160 --> 43:40.440
They said, “She has no Rolls Royce,

43:41.000 --> 43:43.480
She doesn’t take any money,” so they said, “We are not interested.”

43:44.120 --> 43:47.080
It’s a pop show going on, you see, how much money you make

43:47.120 --> 43:48.280
in this guru business.

