If somebody is a smart one, if he has made a big money,

43:51.400 --> 43:53.480
“Oh, he’s a smart fellow, he’s made so much money.”

43:54.080 --> 43:56.480
Can you imagine how money-oriented they are?

43:56.480 --> 44:01.000
You’re not, you are much better. So keep to your styles and I’m sure

44:01.080 --> 44:05.040
British will one day teach all of them a proper thing which is

44:05.080 --> 44:07.560
called is the proper balanced spiritual life.

