I’m not so good but I can speak English and you should not mind

44:15.320 --> 44:18.480
if I have made any mistakes in English language. But one thing

44:18.480 --> 44:22.480
is there that English is much better than many other foreign languages

44:23.040 --> 44:26.080
because I find there is no word for awareness in French,

44:26.160 --> 44:29.280
how to translate awareness. There’s no word for conscience,

44:29.320 --> 44:32.440
there’s no word for consciousness, there’s only one ‘conscia’,

44:33.000 --> 44:35.520
whatever you call it. Of course English also has little problems.

44:36.080 --> 44:39.320
Like for spirit, you call the spirit that is dead the spirit,

44:39.400 --> 44:45.560
then you call the spirit that you get in the pubs also the spirit

44:48.160 --> 44:52.080
and also you call the spirit, that’s the pure thing within yourself,

44:52.120 --> 44:56.240
the reflection of God as spirit, and also the Holy Ghost as the Spirit.

44:56.400 --> 45:02.240
But in Sanskrit language, because it deals more, more with the roots

45:02.240 --> 45:05.120
it has more words for all these things.

45:05.240 --> 45:10.040
But it may not have so many words for the use of the, say,

45:10.080 --> 45:14.280
a glass and the tumbler for this kind of a wine and that,

45:14.320 --> 45:17.280
that it may not have anything about it, it’s a general thing,

45:17.320 --> 45:22.320
what we call as one word for the whole. All pubs are one word

45:22.400 --> 45:27.240
and all alcohols and everything is one word.

45:27.280 --> 45:30.560
There’s no differentiation at all because they do not know this area

45:31.080 --> 45:33.480
but the area they know, for that, they have different words.

45:33.520 --> 45:37.240
And that’s why sometimes one has to take to Sanskrit language

45:37.280 --> 45:41.240
in a way to understand. But you need not worry because we can do it

45:41.280 --> 45:45.120
in English language also very well now, it’s very simple.

45:45.320 --> 45:50.080
Now the happening takes place and then you become empowered

45:50.160 --> 45:53.480
and then you should only learn to maneuver it.

45:54.080 --> 45:57.080
So the yoga has two meanings, the first one means

45:57.080 --> 45:58.400
the union with the Divine,

45:58.480 --> 46:02.240
it is ‘sahaja’ meaning spontaneous because in the modern times

46:02.280 --> 46:06.480
there are all kinds of yogas. So it is a spontaneous, living yoga

46:07.000 --> 46:10.320
and that’s the only one is the real yoga, the rest is all

46:10.440 --> 46:14.520
something like an exercise. And the second part of the yoga means

46:15.080 --> 46:19.240
that the deftness to know the art of handling this power.

46:19.280 --> 46:22.280
That’s why they said when they got their realization or

46:22.320 --> 46:25.480
when they got the blessings of the Holy Spirit they started moving

46:25.480 --> 46:29.240
their hands in such a way that people thought that they were mad,

46:29.360 --> 46:32.280
but the whole of Namaz itself is awakening of the Kundalini,

46:32.400 --> 46:36.080
the whole of Namaz is. And the way we move our hands, you see,

46:36.080 --> 46:39.320
the power moves through our hands. So the movement of our hands

46:39.440 --> 46:43.400
gives us the empowering and we know how to handle this power

46:43.400 --> 46:46.480
within ourselves so you become your own guru.

