Now as I’m here for the first time I would like you to ask Me questions

46:51.080 --> 46:56.040
about Sahaja Yoga, about anything but still I would say you need not

46:56.080 --> 46:59.280
be aggressive with Me because it’s not good and don’t waste the energy

46:59.320 --> 47:02.480
of other people because there are many people who are seekers here

47:02.480 --> 47:05.480
I can see very clearly writ large on their faces,

47:06.000 --> 47:09.240
they’re real seekers of ages and let them have their seeking.

47:09.320 --> 47:13.480
Now if you have any such questions which you want to ask

47:14.080 --> 47:16.480
you can ask Me because in a short lecture like this,

47:16.480 --> 47:20.360
in one visit what could I do, how much could I tell you?

47:20.480 --> 47:24.280
I must have given at least two thousand lectures in English language

47:24.400 --> 47:27.320
and they are all on the tapes and later on you can get them

47:27.360 --> 47:30.080
and listen to them, the nature of the Spirit,

47:30.160 --> 47:32.200
what it means to be realized,

47:32.280 --> 47:40.000
how we become the citizens of God’s kingdom, what is God’s kingdom

47:40.000 --> 47:44.080
within us, where are these chakras placed, everything I’ve told

47:44.200 --> 47:47.400
and everything is to be told to you. There are some books also

