It’s like the sun shining saying, “I’m shining,”

49:03.200 --> 49:06.000
I mean it has to shine jolly well, that’s its nature,

49:06.120 --> 49:10.040
and we have to get the sunshine, jolly well.

49:11.320 --> 49:13.520
It just works spontaneously.

