49:26.480 --> 49:29.240
how many types of yoga do you have?)

49:31.080 --> 49:34.320
I don’t know, as many brains there are in this world,

49:34.320 --> 49:36.680
but there’s only one yoga, is Sahaja.

49:37.200 --> 49:40.360
If you read the Patanjali Yoga from which this so-called yoga has come,

49:40.440 --> 49:44.480
has got ahstangas eight folds, out of which a wee bit

49:44.600 --> 49:48.480
is called as yamanyama, in that a wee bit is the exercises.

49:49.000 --> 49:52.360
But these exercises are of no use without the Kundalini awakening.

49:52.400 --> 49:56.080
It’s written very clearly but nobody reads that big book, you see.

49:56.280 --> 49:58.560
Somebody has read only the beginning of it

49:58.680 --> 50:01.080
and has started calling it yoga.

50:01.320 --> 50:05.400
Now you have to make the Kundalini start

50:05.520 --> 50:07.480
and then you know where the problem is,

50:07.640 --> 50:10.160
for example, you have a problem in the stomach

50:10.360 --> 50:13.600
and if you are doing the exercise of the neck what’s the use.

50:14.400 --> 50:17.280
But the way people do sometimes it frightens Me;

50:17.400 --> 50:20.000
they want to take out the whole of their intestines outside,

50:20.040 --> 50:23.520
the way they are at it, it’s too much. There’s no need to do all that

50:23.680 --> 50:26.480
because that will really give you a heart attack or something like that.

50:26.480 --> 50:29.200
It gives Me a terrible fright;

50:31.080 --> 50:36.240
yoga doesn’t mean exercise by any chance, it means giving relief

50:36.320 --> 50:40.080
to a particular center which is obstructed, and how to do it,

50:40.080 --> 50:44.400
we also do exercises whenever it is needed to a particular thing

50:44.400 --> 50:49.320
but it’s very simple one, once in a while. It’s not like madness all the time,

50:49.320 --> 50:51.200
even people who do yoga I’ve seen,

50:51.280 --> 50:53.480
they cannot sit for one minute straight, you see.

50:53.600 --> 50:58.040
They just go into all these tantrums, it’s very difficult to understand.

50:58.240 --> 51:01.600
You become very normal, decent people.

51:03.560 --> 51:06.360
So the other yogas I don't know what they are all like,

51:06.480 --> 51:09.240
Kundalini yoga you can call it, is the Kundalini yoga

51:09.280 --> 51:11.560
if you want elaborately say it, Kundalini Yoga,

51:11.640 --> 51:15.480
it's Sahaja Yoga or you can call it Yoga itself.

51:17.680 --> 51:20.240
But I have called it Sahaja is not the point

51:20.360 --> 51:22.400
is a word very ancient Sahaja Saha-ja,

51:22.440 --> 51:27.080
'Saha' means with, 'ja' means born, it's born with you

51:28.600 --> 51:32.280
Like every seed can become a tree, it is born with you,

51:32.400 --> 51:36.440
you all can become that tree of life.

